#local.example
    h3#locale Localization
    p
        | Flatpickr has been translated to
        a(href='https://github.com/chmln/flatpickr/tree/gh-pages/src', target='_blank') over 25 languages
        | .
    p
        | Localization involves simply overriding objects below, contained in
        code Flatpickr.l10n
        | .
    p
        strong Locale:

        select#locales
            option(value='') English
    p
        input#locale_calendar.flatpickr(type='text', data-inline='true', data-min-date='today')
    table.table
        thead
            tr
                th Property
                th Type
                th Default
                th Description
        tbody
            tr
                td l10n.weekdays.shorthand
                td array
